<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text"><i>Elymus glaucus </i>sprouts from surviving stolons and tillers after fires (Johnson 1999). It establishes quickly after low- to moderate-intensity fire and may form an early seral type in recently burned woodlands.</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
